# TUFF-RADICAL Global Environment
# NOTE: Removed hardcoded Intel driver overrides to ensure AMD/Hybrid compatibility.

# Global hardware acceleration settings
# Drivers are now handled by mesa-va-drivers / mesa-vdpau-drivers auto-selection.
